-- INSTANT VIEW: Bernanke says 2nd stimulus likely needed
-- 
-- Mon Oct 20, 2008 10:16am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/10/20/us-usa-economy-bernanke-idUSTRE49J4ZN20081020

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - U.S. Federal Reserve Chairman 

 Ben Bernanke told Congress on Monday that another wave of government spending may be needed as the economy limps through what could be an extended period of subpar growth.